title: Thelma Retreat Wholefood Teahouse
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Western, Bakery, Australian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Organic teas and coffee, baked goods made with organic flour ground daily in a stone mill; can make snack, breakfast, and lunch specially for vegans (prior booking is suggested if you are in a hurry). Uses local produce and organic, even from its own garden. Situated at the end of a country lane in a large garden.
